Package herencia

Class Schedule

  • java.lang.Object
    • herencia.Schedule
  • public class Schedule
extends java.lang.Object
    The Schedule class represents a schedule entry, including the day, start and end hours, and a unique identifier for the schedule. This class provides constructors, getter and setter methods for each property, and a toString method for easy representation of a Schedule object.
